quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  12,7,"Mu by’ukuri, (inkuru) ya Yusufu n'abavandimwe be irimo inyigisho ku babaza (bakeneye kumenya)"
  12,8,"Wibuke ubwo (abavandimwe ba Yusufu) bavugaga bati \"Rwose Yusufu n’umuvandimwe we (Benjamini) ni bo batoni kuri data kuturusha, nyamara ari twe benshi (tunafite imbaraga). Mu by’ukuri, data yarakosheje mu buryo bugaragara"
  12,9,"(Baravuga bati) \"Nimwice Yusufu cyangwa mumute ishyanga, bizatuma so abakunda. Maze nyuma y’aho (muzicuze) mube abantu beza"
  12,10,"Umwe muri bo aravuga ati \"Ntimwice Yusufu, ahubwo mumunage mu iriba azatoragurwe na bamwe mu bagenzi, niba koko (mwagambiriye) kubikora"
  12,11,"(Bamaze kunoza umugambi begerase) baramubwira bati \"Dawe! Kuki utatugirira icyizere (cyo kujyana na) Yusufu kandi mu by’ukuri tumwifuriza ibyiza"
  12,12,"Ejo uzamureke tujyane yidagadure anakine, kandi rwose tuzamurinda (ntacyo azaba)"
  12,13,"(Se) aravuga ati \"Mu by’ukuri, naterwa agahinda no kuba mwamujyana (kure yanjye), ndanatinya ko mwarangara imbwebwe ikamurya"
  12,14,"Baravuga bati \"Mu by’ukuri, imbwebwe iramutse imuriye (duhari) turi benshi (tunafite imbaraga), twaba turi abanyagihombo"
  12,15,"Maze bamujyanye, bemeranywa kumujugunya mu iriba, nukoturamuhishurira tuti \"Rwose (hari igihe) uzababwira iby’iki gikorwa cyabo batazi (ko ari wowe)"
  12,16,Nuko ku mugoroba (barataha) bagera kuri se barira
  12,17,"Baravuga bati \"Dawe! Mu by'ukuri, twagiye kurushanwa (kwiruka no gutera amacumu) dusiga Yusufu ku bintu byacu maze imbwebwe iramurya; ariko ntiwakwemera ibyo tukubwira kabone n’iyo twaba tuvuga ukuri"
  12,18,"Banazana ikanzu ye iriho amaraso atari ay’ukuri. (Se) arababwira ati \"Ahubwo imitima yanyu yabashishikarije kugirira nabi (Yusufu mubigeraho). Bityo, kwihangana ni byo byiza (kuri njye). Kandi Allahni we wo kwishingikirizwa mu byo muvuga"
  12,19,"Nuko haza abagenzi bohereza umuvomyi wabo (kubavomera amazi mu iriba), maze amanuye indobo ye (mu iriba, azamuramo Yusufu); aravuga ati \"Mbega inkuru nziza! Dore umwana w’umuhungu!\" Nuko bamuhisha (bagenzi babo) bamugira igicuruzwa. Kandi Allah ni Umumenyi uhebuje w'ibyo bakoze"
  12,20,Nuko bamugurisha ku giciro gito; amadirihamu make. Kandi nta gaciro bamuhaga